{"title":"String字符串与字符(char类型)数组互相转换","date":"2018-10-10T04:04:23.000Z","link":"post/270","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:41:27.774Z","content":"<h3 id=\"1-String类的toCharArray-方法，将字符串转为字符-char-数组\">1.String类的toCharArray()方法，将字符串转为字符(char)数组<a href=\"post/270#1-String类的toCharArray-方法，将字符串转为字符-char-数组\"></a></h3>  <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String ss=”abc”; </span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">char</span>[] cc; </span><br><span class=\"line\">  cc=ss.toCharArray(); </span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">//这时cc=&#123;‘a’,’b’,’c’&#125;；</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-String类的valueOf-方法，将字符-char-数组转换为字符串\">2.String类的valueOf()方法，将字符(char)数组转换为字符串<a href=\"post/270#2-String类的valueOf-方法，将字符-char-数组转换为字符串\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span>[] cc=&#123;‘a’,’b’,’c’&#125;; </span><br><span class=\"line\">ss=String.valueOf(cc); </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//这时ss=“abc”；</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"开发中常遇到到的问题:java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException","link":"post/271"},"next":{"title":"Java数据类型中String、Integer、int相互间的转换","link":"post/269"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/270/"}